        "product_description": {
            "value": "The ASR Tactical Kevlar Trip Wire delivers reliable performance in a lightweight, durable package. This 85-foot spool of black Kevlar cord offers an impressive 84 lb tensile strength, making it ideal for tactical, survival, and outdoor applications. The high-strength Kevlar construction resists cutting, stretching, and abrasion while remaining thin and discreet for effective trip line setups. Its black color helps the line blend into surroundings, and the convenient spool keeps the wire tangle-free and easy to deploy. Whether used for perimeter awareness, camp security, or general utility, this trip wire provides dependable, low-visibility coverage in a compact form.",
